sentences: Birge Lønquist Hansen (6 November 1945 – 27 August 2004), better known as Jodle Birge, was a Danish composer and singer.
From 1992 to 2001 there was a museum for Jodle Birge in Silkeborg in Denmark.
A new and bigger museum was opened on 22 July 2005.
